name: Swamp
LocationDStext: To initiate battle here, you must use +3 Force. You may not 'react' to or from here. May not be deployed to Bespin, Coruscant, Hoth, Kessel or Tatooine.
LocationLStext: Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one creature here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. May not be deployed to Bespin, Coruscant, Hoth, Kessel or Tatooine.
